flowchart TD
    A[CLI python -m benchmarks.run_custom] -->|args seeds/tasks/splits/warm-splits| B[load_tasks from benchmarks/tasks]
    B -->|domain task lists| C[Loop domains and seeds]

    C --> D[Control Arm]
    D -->|system prompt + task prompt| E[call_agent litellm]
    E -->|response usage latency| F[score via graders]
    F -->|record row| G[append control record]

    C --> H[Treatment Arm]
    H -->|initialize LearnKit sqlite db| I[warm phase optional]
    I -->|warm task prompts| J[memory.agent ask]
    J -->|distilled memory persisted| K[scored treatment loop]
    K -->|response + attribution + context chars| F
    F -->|record row| L[append treatment record]

    G --> M[summarize]
    L --> M
    M -->|raw rows| N[results run_id raw.json]
    M -->|aggregates| O[results run_id summary.json]
    M -->|human report| P[results run_id summary.md]
    M -->|time series| Q[results run_id compounding.csv]
    N -->|post hoc| R[attribution_summary.py]
    R -->|harmful_retrieval_rate wrong_primary_rate| S[contamination diagnostics]
